 company is also engaged in molecular design and synthesis purification advanced analytics formulation development and containers and delivery systems for the handling of high purity materials to deliver solutions and process support to its customersmaterialsthe materials segment provides the global semiconductor industry with high purity process materials for deposition metallization chamber cleaning and etching chemicals mechanical planarization slurries organosilanes organometallics and liquid dopants for thin film deposition and formulated chemical products for postetch cleaning primarily for the manufacture of silicon and compound semiconductors and thin film transistor liquid crystal displays the materials segment offerings for deposition chemical mechanical planarization cmp etching doping and cleaning enable semiconductor manufacturers to create devices for both the logic and memory market segments its product categories include advanced materials and process materials advanced materials supplies products and services through advanced deposition materials adm planarization pla products and surface prep and clean spc formulated products platforms pla products include cmp slurries and post cmp cleans that are used to prepare chips with deposited thin films for the next stage of fabrication spc formulated products are designed to selectively etch and remove debris and contamination during various stages of the wafer fabrication processprocess materials supplies products such as highpurity gases and chemicals utilized in the processes of cleaning etching doping and film deposition for its semiconductor displays and light emitting diode led customers the cleaning and etchant gases such as nitrogen trifluoride nf and hexafluorobutadiene cf are used for chamber cleaning and etching applications in the production of semiconductors its process gases for deposition and metallization such as tungsten hexafluoride wf are used in the process of depositing film layers its dopants such as arsine ash are used for ion implantation for semiconductors and its hydride gases such as ammonia nh support applications in display and leds its process materials products are used in a range of displays including televisions tvs mobile and touch displays automotive applications and other ledbased displays and logic and memory technology the company supplies these products to its customers throughout the united states europe and asia as of september   the materials segment operated  production and six research and development facilities and served over  customersdelivery systems and servicesthe dss segment provides turnkey installation services during facility construction and startup as well as onsite operating services its product categories include equipment gas and chemical delivery systems installation turnkey and installation and onsite services megasys it develops designs manufactures and sells bulk gas specialty gas and specialty chemical cabinets and systems it also provides flow and temperature control systems and analytical systems to capture key data for its customers it offers resources to assist a new semiconductor fabrication in the design installation startup and commissioning of the gases and specialty materials delivery systems and quality assurance in addition it sells spare parts equipment upgrades equipment maintenance and provide trainingthe company offers onsite services to assist its customers in managing their inventory of gases and chemicals including ordering product changes and monitoring quality assurance operating its delivery systems and managing the bulk gas and specialty gas operations as of september   the dss segment operated three production facilities with two in the united states and one in asiathe company competes with adeka air liquide cabot microelectronics dow chemical entegris fujifilm hyosung jsr microelectronics merck em and sk materials » full overview of vsm company address versum materials inc  s rive